{"tid":774151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"專家指土瓜灣站附近漏煤氣引致爆炸機會不大","createTime":"2018-08-10T05:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T05:51:54.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b2c55cdc809d59650bfcc7b1d676ed2910fcbc","tid":774151,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:47:08.000Z","msg":"專家指土瓜灣站附近漏煤氣引致爆炸機會不大<br />\n2018-08-10 HKT 12:44<br />\n<br />\n港鐵昨晚證實，前年已發現土瓜灣站7個喉管位置的沉降幅度達至需要跟進的指標，並承認其中3個未有通報煤氣公司。<br />\n<br />\n香港管綫專業學會前會長黃敬表示，港鐵沙中綫土瓜灣站的沉降事件，如果達至氣體洩漏指標，應該要採取相應行動，煤氣濃度達至大氣的10%才會發生爆炸，但一般情況下一旦發現煤氣洩漏，都能夠在10分鐘內關閉氣體閥門，相信突然爆炸的機會不大。<br />\n<br />\n黃敬指出，煤氣管道一般會埋在地下1米深左右，如果發現泥土沉降，可以用「回填」等方式加固，避免管道受到破壞。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411662-20180810.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411662-20180810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=oHw83IesGPoPlBdW0TbFUP7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=8bab2fd4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1411662-20180810.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=1c8cc395\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1411662-20180810.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"329c06f936c2ff5032baf69c6e6c8313e11598e4","tid":774151,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"咁之前台灣呢？"},{"pid":"409fd0acfad619f701e1b5ab6506a94c2cf81b98","tid":774151,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:51:02.000Z","msg":"機會不大都係有機會"},{"pid":"e4d74e623bacaffd54fdd83cca4a5bbf8b83f757","tid":774151,"uid":10637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"329c06f936c2ff5032baf69c6e6c8313e11598e4","tid":774151,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"咁之前台灣呢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"香港唔同台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}